caption.title: Phylogenetic tree of the DENV-2 based on the E gene sequences.
caption.p: Complete E gene sequences were used to construct the phylogenetic tree with General Time Reversible (GTR) substitution model using the MEGA7 software [ 26]. Red- DENV-2 sequence from Singapore, Blue- Generated E gene sequences from the positive mosquito pools. Sequences retrieved from GenBank are shown with accession numbers.
